#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn13.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn13.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 13 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 13 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "1. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn13.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Dutiyasamuddasutta "
msgstr "8. The Ocean (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn13.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.8:1.2"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, mahāsamuddo parikkhayaṃ pariyādānaṃ gaccheyya, ṭhapetvā dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose the water in the ocean dried up and evaporated except for two or three drops. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.8:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn13.8:1.4"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yaṃ vā mahāsamudde udakaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ yāni vā dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni avasiṭṭhānī”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the water in the ocean that has dried up and evaporated, or the two or three drops left?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn13.8:2.1"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ mahāsamudde udakaṃ, yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ; "
msgstr "“Sir, the water in the ocean that has dried up and evaporated is certainly more. "

msgctxt "sn13.8:2.2"
msgid "appamattakāni dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni avasiṭṭhāni. "
msgstr "The two or three drops left are tiny. "

msgctxt "sn13.8:2.3"
msgid "Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti mahāsamudde udakaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ upanidhāya dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni avasiṭṭhānī”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the water in the ocean that has dried up and evaporated, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred thousandth part.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.8:2.4"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe … "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple, the suffering that’s over and done with is more …” "

msgctxt "sn13.8:2.5"
msgid "dhammacakkhupaṭilābho”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn13.8:2.6"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

